# Start or stop juice/liquid reward delivery via solenoid valve.
# Served by: teensy node (firmware, service ~/set_reward) / mock_teensy node.
# Called by: TeensyInterface.set_reward() (interfaces/teensy.py).

# --- Request ---
bool activate                        # True to open the reward solenoid; False to close it immediately
builtin_interfaces/Duration duration # Required when activate=True: how long the solenoid stays open (seconds); must be > 0; ignored when activate=False
---
# --- Response ---
bool success    # True if the command succeeded; False if duration is missing on activate or non-zero on deactivate
string message  # Human-readable confirmation or error (e.g. "Reward started for 0.300 s")
